# Benchmark Scenarios

This directory is reserved for Phase 13.5.6.2 — API Benchmarking.

Each file here will export a scenario object:

```js
export const scenario = {
  name: 'books-list',
  request: async () => httpClient.request('GET', `${benchmarkConfig.baseUrl}/books`),
};
```

Scenario files added here will be picked up by a Phase 13.5.6.2 runner
that iterates all concurrencyLevels from benchmarkConfig.
